OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FTemperatures are set to drop by up to
OL,7,F15C in just one week for some parts of
OL,8,Fthe UK as average temperatures and
OL,9,Fprolonged, heavy showers replace the
OL,10,Fhistoric heatwave.
OL,12,FThis abrupt change comes as Monday
OL,13,Fmarks the official start of
OL,14,Fmeteorological summer.
OL,16,FWhy are we seeing such a big change in
OL,17,Fthe weather?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780333562
OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FThe high pressure, which gave us the
OL,7,Fvery settled and sunny spell of hot
OL,8,Fweather, drawing in a feed of very
OL,9,Fwarm air from the south, has now moved
OL,10,Faway.
OL,12,FThe Atlantic will be the main driver
OL,13,Fof our weather over the coming week,
OL,14,Fwith a mainly westerly wind pulling in
OL,15,Fmoist, cooler air along with rain-
OL,16,Fbearing frontal systems.
OL,18,FOverall, expect a very unsettled week
OL,19,Fwith rain never too far away.
OL,21,FHow cold will it get?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780333562
OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FWell, compared to last week's record-
OL,7,Fbreaking temperatures, it will feel
OL,8,Fcold - although in real terms we're
OL,9,Factually just talking about values
OL,10,Fthat are around the seasonal average;
OL,11,Fwidely 14-17C in the north and 16-19C
OL,12,Fin the south.
OL,14,FHow much rain will we see?
OL,16,FNot enough to make up for the fact
OL,17,Fthat it's been so dry, for so long,
OL,18,Ffor many parts of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780333562
OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FNorthern and western parts of the UK
OL,7,Fare expected to see the most frequent
OL,8,Fand heaviest rain, with some showers
OL,9,Fpotentially turning heavy and thundery.
OL,11,FShowers or showery bands of rain are
OL,12,Fexpected in the south and south east
OL,13,Ftoo (with only 30% of the expected
OL,14,Frain falling here last month, this is
OL,15,Fnow desperately needed).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780333562
OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FBut the very nature of showers is
OL,7,Fthat, unlike an organised band of rain
OL,8,Fthat marches across the country,
OL,9,Fshowers can be very localised - so
OL,10,Fmany areas may end up with a largely
OL,11,Fdry week.
OL,13,FHowever, the unstable atmosphere over
OL,14,Fthe coming few days is one where
OL,15,Fshowers should form readily, so, after
OL,16,Fsuch a long dry spell, there is at
OL,17,Fleast a high probability that there
OL,18,Fwill be some relief for all farmers
OL,19,Fand growers this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
