CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780333562
OL,3,CWeather whiplash: Heatwave ends as wet
OL,4,Cand windy conditions sweep in
OL,6,FIs there any sign of summery weather
OL,7,Freturning?
OL,9,FYes! It's too early for details, but
OL,10,Fthe Met Office are signalling that
OL,11,Fdrier weather may start to become more
OL,12,Fdominant through the second week of
OL,13,FJune.
OL,15,FWith high pressure looking to build in
OL,16,Fagain from the middle of the month,
OL,17,Fthe return of some very warm weather
OL,18,Fis becoming an increasing possibility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
